PEOPLE
v.
MOORE S243387 Supreme Court of California SEPTEMBER 13, 2017 Votes: Cantil-Sakauye, C.J., Chin, Corrigan, Liu, Cuéllar and Kruger, JJ.

Review is ordered on the court's own motion. Defendant is deemed the petitioner in this court. ( Cal. Rules of Court, rule 8.520(a)(6).) Further action in this matter is deferred pending consideration and disposition of a related issue in People v. Ruiz, S235556 (see Cal. Rules of Court, rule 8.512(d)(2) ), or pending further order of the court. Submission of additional briefing, pursuant to California Rules of Court, rule 8.520, is deferred pending further order of the court.
